#: ../../../doc/en/announce/release-2.8.6.rst:2
msgid "pytest-2.8.6"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../doc/en/announce/release-2.8.6.rst:4
msgid ""
"pytest is a mature Python testing tool with more than 1100 tests against "
"itself, passing on many different interpreters and platforms. This release "
"is supposed to be drop-in compatible to 2.8.5."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../doc/en/announce/release-2.8.6.rst:8
msgid "See below for the changes and see docs at:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../doc/en/announce/release-2.8.6.rst:10
msgid "http://pytest.org"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../doc/en/announce/release-2.8.6.rst:12
msgid "As usual, you can upgrade from pypi via::"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../doc/en/announce/release-2.8.6.rst:14
msgid "pip install -U pytest"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../doc/en/announce/release-2.8.6.rst:16
msgid "Thanks to all who contributed to this release, among them:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../doc/en/announce/release-2.8.6.rst:18
msgid ""
"AMiT Kumar Bruno Oliveira Erik M. Bray Florian Bruhin Georgy Dyuldin Jeff "
"Widman Kartik Singhal Loïc Estève Manu Phatak Peter Demin Rick van Hattem "
"Ronny Pfannschmidt Ulrich Petri foxx"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../doc/en/announce/release-2.8.6.rst:34
msgid "Happy testing, The py.test Development Team"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../doc/en/announce/release-2.8.6.rst:39
msgid "2.8.6 (compared to 2.8.5)"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../doc/en/announce/release-2.8.6.rst:41
msgid ""
"fix #1259: allow for double nodeids in junitxml, this was a regression "
"failing plugins combinations like pytest-pep8 + pytest-flakes"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../doc/en/announce/release-2.8.6.rst:45
msgid ""
"Workaround for exception that occurs in pyreadline when using ``--pdb`` with "
"standard I/O capture enabled. Thanks Erik M. Bray for the PR."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../doc/en/announce/release-2.8.6.rst:49
msgid ""
"fix #900: Better error message in case the target of a ``monkeypatch`` call "
"raises an ``ImportError``."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../doc/en/announce/release-2.8.6.rst:52
msgid ""
"fix #1292: monkeypatch calls (setattr, setenv, etc.) are now O(1). Thanks "
"David R. MacIver for the report and Bruno Oliveira for the PR."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../doc/en/announce/release-2.8.6.rst:55
msgid ""
"fix #1223: captured stdout and stderr are now properly displayed before "
"entering pdb when ``--pdb`` is used instead of being thrown away. Thanks Cal "
"Leeming for the PR."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../doc/en/announce/release-2.8.6.rst:59
msgid ""
"fix #1305: pytest warnings emitted during ``pytest_terminal_summary`` are "
"now properly displayed. Thanks Ionel Maries Cristian for the report and "
"Bruno Oliveira for the PR."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../doc/en/announce/release-2.8.6.rst:63
msgid ""
"fix #628: fixed internal UnicodeDecodeError when doctests contain unicode. "
"Thanks Jason R. Coombs for the report and Bruno Oliveira for the PR."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../doc/en/announce/release-2.8.6.rst:66
msgid ""
"fix #1334: Add captured stdout to jUnit XML report on setup error. Thanks "
"Georgy Dyuldin for the PR."
msgstr ""
